01:01:35.600 --> 01:01:37.296
And if you force pressure up that tube,

01:01:37.296 --> 01:01:39.550
you're going to be
putting more air pressure

01:01:39.550 --> 01:01:41.150
into the compartment.

01:01:41.150 --> 01:01:42.308
- To counter it.

01:01:42.308 --> 01:01:45.540
- If it's not enough and if you're sucking

01:01:45.540 --> 01:01:46.500
you're going the other way.

01:01:46.500 --> 01:01:49.130
In reality, I think as long
